responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "F2CB9A524D9FF775A40E1B8DD41B35E1", "I\'m following the local minotaur tribe, the Ashen Flame. It seems that they\'ve been living here in the Riverlands since the time of the Harbingers. They arrived hence to fight for the Harrower, alongside the goblins and other foul folk. Now, though, they seem at odds with everyone but themselves. I want to know why.")
